headline: Stifel Reaffirms Buy Rating on Accenture After Q3 Earnings Beat and Solid Growth
summary: Accenture plc (NYSE:ACN) ranks among the best fundamental stocks to buy according to hedge funds. On June 23, Stifel reaffirmed its $355 price target and Buy rating for Accenture plc (NYSE:ACN) in response to the company’s fiscal third-quarter results. Accenture’s fiscal third-quarter results exceeded expectations, with earnings per share growing 13% against the consensus forecast […]
